[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1782},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20221215\u002F2411869749\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20221215\u002F2411869749\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20221215\u002F2411869749\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20221215\u002F2411869749\u002F":1757,"related:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20221215\u002F2411869749\u002F":1766},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2022\u002F12\u002F15\u002Fdiscord-bot-with-openai-gpt3\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1740,"date":1741,"description":18,"extension":1742,"lang":1743,"meta":1744,"navigation":392,"path":1745,"readingMinutes":1746,"seo":1747,"standalone":1748,"stem":1749,"tags":1750,"tldr":1753,"updated":1754,"url":1755,"__hash__":1756},"content\u002FNodejs\u002F用-OpenAI-GPT-3-建立一個-Discord-聊天機器人.md","用 OpenAI GPT-3 建立一個 Discord 聊天機器人","2411869749",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1726},"minimark",[11,15,19,39,42,45,48,64,67,71,81,88,91,97,100,106,114,117,123,126,132,135,141,144,150,153,156,164,167,170,176,179,185,188,191,197,202,205,208,211,254,257,283,304,307,310,313,316,321,324,585,588,619,634,637,656,683,887,897,903,906,910,927,1270,1273,1295,1304,1316,1565,1572,1578,1583,1587,1590,1598,1601,1610,1613,1619,1622,1625,1628,1631,1634,1641,1644,1647,1670,1673,1676,1679,1694,1703,1714,1722],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"這一篇將會來介紹如何使用 OpenAI GPT-3 來建立一個 Discord 聊天機器人，並且讓它可以回應我們的訊息，而且你會發現 Discord 非常適合拿來串 OpenAI，雖然主軸是以 GPT-3 為主，但是我的範例程式碼也有提供 GPT-3.5 的 Commit 給予參考唷~",[20,21,22],"blockquote",{},[16,23,24,28,29,32,33,38],{},[25,26,27],"strong",{},"Warning","\n請注意，本篇",[25,30,31],{},"必須自己申請 OpenAI Key","，申請流程可詳見",[34,35,37],"a",{"href":36},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20221210\u002F1224824056\u002F#%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-OpenAI-API","這一篇","文章",[12,40,41],{"id":41},"事前說明",[16,43,44],{},"這一篇將不會有過多的著墨說明 Node.js、Git、GitHub、npm 等等的基礎知識，因為如果包含這些的話這一篇內容可能會多。",[16,46,47],{},"但是如果你對於 npm 與 Git 指令不熟悉的話，這邊我倒是可以提供自己先前的一些文章給予參考",[49,50,51,58],"ul",{},[52,53,54],"li",{},[34,55,57],{"href":56},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200921\u002F849819598\u002F","(8) 試著學 Hexo - 你應該懂基本的 npm 指令",[52,59,60],{},[34,61,63],{"href":62},"\u002Fgit\u002F20190615\u002F1148594701\u002F","基礎 Git 指令",[16,65,66],{},"當然結尾我也會附上範例程式碼的 GitHub 連結，到時候我也會針對 README 進行一些說明，方便你可以快速運作一個 Discord 機器人。",[12,68,70],{"id":69},"discord-準備動作","Discord 準備動作",[16,72,73,74,80],{},"首先第一個步驟是我們要先去建立一個 Discord 機器人，首先請你先到 ",[34,75,79],{"href":76,"rel":77},"https:\u002F\u002Fdiscord.com\u002Fdevelopers\u002Fapplications",[78],"nofollow","Discord Developer Portal"," 頁面點選 Application",[16,82,83],{},[84,85],"img",{"alt":86,"src":87},"Application","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fa0Od41t.png",[16,89,90],{},"然後點選 「New Application」",[16,92,93],{},[84,94],{"alt":95,"src":96},"New Application","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FaEa0M5F.png",[16,98,99],{},"接著會要求你輸入這個機器人的名稱，這邊我們就叫做「OpenAI GPT-3」吧",[16,101,102],{},[84,103],{"alt":104,"src":105},"OpenAI GPT-3","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FcFSnLzP.png",[20,107,108],{},[16,109,110,113],{},[25,111,112],{},"Note","\n請注意，這個應用程式的名稱不是機器人的名稱，除此之外到時候這個應用程式名稱也會變成 Discord 伺服器的權限名稱，所以請記得要取一個好的名稱。",[16,115,116],{},"進到「OpenAI GPT-3」應用程式頁面後，我們要先去建立一個機器人，點選左邊的「Bot」",[16,118,119],{},[84,120],{"alt":121,"src":122},"Bot","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FbaUchls.png",[16,124,125],{},"然後再點右邊「Add Bot」",[16,127,128],{},[84,129],{"alt":130,"src":131},"Add Bot","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FvnpXA5Y.png",[16,133,134],{},"當你按下「Add Bot」後，Discord 會要求你確認是否要建立一個機器人，點選「Yes, do it!」",[16,136,137],{},[84,138],{"alt":139,"src":140},"Yes, do it!","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FN6LdkrN.png",[16,142,143],{},"接著下方就會出現你的機器人，這邊請你找到「Token」的欄位，並且按一下「Reset Token」",[16,145,146],{},[84,147],{"alt":148,"src":149},"Reset Token","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FA5iTEwZ.png",[16,151,152],{},"這時候你會取得一串 Token，這串 Token 就是你的機器人的 Token，請記得要把它記下來，因為之後我們會用到它。",[16,154,155],{},"請不要隨意將你的機器人 Token 分享給別人，因為這樣會讓別人可以控制你的機器人。",[16,157,158,159,163],{},"除此之外，這邊 ",[160,161,162],"code",{},"Username"," 將會是你的機器人的名稱，在最後的範例程式碼，我是把它叫做「妙麗·格蘭傑」就是了。",[16,165,166],{},"接著這邊有一件事情很重要，麻煩滾到下方一點的地方找到「Privileged Gateway Intents」，然後把「Message Content Intent」打開，這樣才能讓機器人可以接收到訊息唷！",[16,168,169],{},"接著呢？我們要去把這個機器人加入到我們的 Discord 伺服器中，點選左邊的「OAuth2」，然後再選「URL Generator」的方式（比較簡單）",[16,171,172],{},[84,173],{"alt":174,"src":175},"URL Generator","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FLtQioGX.png",[16,177,178],{},"進入後，請在左邊的「SCOPES」中勾選「bot」，然後在「BOT PERMISSIONS」中勾選「Send Messages」",[16,180,181],{},[84,182],{"alt":183,"src":184},"Send Messages","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FeiUZwyz.png",[16,186,187],{},"由於我們只是要讓機器人可以回應我們的訊息，所以我們只勾選「Send Messages」，如果你想要讓機器人可以做更多事情，可以再斟酌一下要勾選哪些權限。",[16,189,190],{},"接著下方你應該就會看到一塊「Generated URL」的區塊，將那一串 URL 複製下來並貼到瀏覽器的網址列上，然後按下 Enter，基本上你應該就會看到選擇要將機器人加入到哪個伺服器的畫面，選擇好你的伺服器後就大膽的把它加入吧！",[16,192,193],{},[84,194],{"alt":195,"src":196},"Add to Bot","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FePRXynz.png",[16,198,199],{},[84,200],{"alt":195,"src":201},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FpbMp7A7.png",[16,203,204],{},"這樣子你的機器人就會進入到你的伺服器了，那麼到這邊為止，我們基本的 Discord 機器人算是建立完成了。",[12,206,207],{"id":207},"建立專案環境",[16,209,210],{},"首先請你先建立一個資料夾，例如...叫做「discord-bot」，然後當然就是初始化這個專案，所以我這邊就快速貼上相關的指令：",[212,213,218],"pre",{"className":214,"code":215,"language":216,"meta":217,"style":217},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","mkdir discord-bot\ncd discord-bot\nnpm init -y\n","bash","",[160,219,220,233,242],{"__ignoreMap":217},[221,222,225,229],"span",{"class":223,"line":224},"line",1,[221,226,228],{"class":227},"s_sBn","mkdir",[221,230,232],{"class":231},"sTRMh"," discord-bot\n",[221,234,236,240],{"class":223,"line":235},2,[221,237,239],{"class":238},"sCcAr","cd",[221,241,232],{"class":231},[221,243,245,248,251],{"class":223,"line":244},3,[221,246,247],{"class":227},"npm",[221,249,250],{"class":231}," init",[221,252,253],{"class":238}," -y\n",[16,255,256],{},"接著我們要來安裝一些我們會使用到的套件",[49,258,259,267,275],{},[52,260,261,262],{},"dotenv\n",[49,263,264],{},[52,265,266],{},"用來讀取 .env 檔案",[52,268,269,270],{},"discord.js\n",[49,271,272],{},[52,273,274],{},"用來操作 Discord 的 套件",[52,276,277,278],{},"openai\n",[49,279,280],{},[52,281,282],{},"用來操作 OpenAI GPT-3 的 套件",[212,284,286],{"className":214,"code":285,"language":216,"meta":217,"style":217},"npm install dotenv discord.js openai\n",[160,287,288],{"__ignoreMap":217},[221,289,290,292,295,298,301],{"class":223,"line":224},[221,291,247],{"class":227},[221,293,294],{"class":231}," install",[221,296,297],{"class":231}," dotenv",[221,299,300],{"class":231}," discord.js",[221,302,303],{"class":231}," openai\n",[16,305,306],{},"接著在專案根目錄建立一個「index.js」的檔案，因為接下來我們會開始在這一個檔案內撰寫我們的機器人程式碼。",[16,308,309],{},"（你也可以考慮加入 ESLint 管理你的程式碼品質唷）",[12,311,312],{"id":312},"撰寫程式碼",[16,314,315],{},"終於到了撰寫程式碼的環節了，那麼這邊可能不會每一行都說明，但會盡可能的簡單一點，讓你可以盡可能做出一個自己的機器人。",[317,318,320],"h3",{"id":319},"discord-機器人","Discord 機器人",[16,322,323],{},"首先，先讓我們撰寫 Discord 的機器人程式碼，那麼在官方 npm 上面，我們可以找到 Discord.js 的使用方式",[212,325,329],{"className":326,"code":327,"language":328,"meta":217,"style":217},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","const { Client, GatewayIntentBits } = require('discord.js');\nconst client = new Client({ intents: [GatewayIntentBits.Guilds] });\n\nclient.on('ready', () => {\n  console.log(`Logged in as ${client.user.tag}!`);\n});\n\nclient.on('interactionCreate', async interaction => {\n  if (!interaction.isChatInputCommand()) return;\n\n  if (interaction.commandName === 'ping') {\n    await interaction.reply('Pong!');\n  }\n});\n\nclient.login(TOKEN);\n","js",[160,330,331,369,388,394,417,450,456,461,486,513,518,535,554,560,565,570],{"__ignoreMap":217},[221,332,333,337,341,344,347,350,353,356,360,363,366],{"class":223,"line":224},[221,334,336],{"class":335},"sWyjQ","const",[221,338,340],{"class":339},"sMAXC"," { ",[221,342,343],{"class":238},"Client",[221,345,346],{"class":339},", ",[221,348,349],{"class":238},"GatewayIntentBits",[221,351,352],{"class":339}," } ",[221,354,355],{"class":335},"=",[221,357,359],{"class":358},"sj_SG"," require",[221,361,362],{"class":339},"(",[221,364,365],{"class":231},"'discord.js'",[221,367,368],{"class":339},");\n",[221,370,371,373,376,379,382,385],{"class":223,"line":235},[221,372,336],{"class":335},[221,374,375],{"class":238}," client",[221,377,378],{"class":335}," =",[221,380,381],{"class":335}," new",[221,383,384],{"class":358}," Client",[221,386,387],{"class":339},"({ intents: [GatewayIntentBits.Guilds] });\n",[221,389,390],{"class":223,"line":244},[221,391,393],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":392},true,"\n",[221,395,397,400,403,405,408,411,414],{"class":223,"line":396},4,[221,398,399],{"class":339},"client.",[221,401,402],{"class":358},"on",[221,404,362],{"class":339},[221,406,407],{"class":231},"'ready'",[221,409,410],{"class":339},", () ",[221,412,413],{"class":335},"=>",[221,415,416],{"class":339}," {\n",[221,418,420,423,426,428,431,434,437,440,442,445,448],{"class":223,"line":419},5,[221,421,422],{"class":339},"  console.",[221,424,425],{"class":358},"log",[221,427,362],{"class":339},[221,429,430],{"class":231},"`Logged in as ${",[221,432,433],{"class":339},"client",[221,435,436],{"class":231},".",[221,438,439],{"class":339},"user",[221,441,436],{"class":231},[221,443,444],{"class":339},"tag",[221,446,447],{"class":231},"}!`",[221,449,368],{"class":339},[221,451,453],{"class":223,"line":452},6,[221,454,455],{"class":339},"});\n",[221,457,459],{"class":223,"line":458},7,[221,460,393],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":392},[221,462,464,466,468,470,473,475,478,481,484],{"class":223,"line":463},8,[221,465,399],{"class":339},[221,467,402],{"class":358},[221,469,362],{"class":339},[221,471,472],{"class":231},"'interactionCreate'",[221,474,346],{"class":339},[221,476,477],{"class":335},"async",[221,479,480],{"class":227}," interaction",[221,482,483],{"class":335}," =>",[221,485,416],{"class":339},[221,487,489,492,495,498,501,504,507,510],{"class":223,"line":488},9,[221,490,491],{"class":335},"  if",[221,493,494],{"class":339}," (",[221,496,497],{"class":335},"